{"tid":1851920,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」今晚有十二個工會擺街站支持醫護罷工！五個工會即場收會員！記得去攞白絲帶！","createTime":"2020-01-30T08:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T03:24:14.000Z","uid":104585,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"33bc2d24082b3c6ea170ca6c73fe9c02ebf9fd98","tid":1851920,"uid":104585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:24:19.000Z","msg":"⚠️【封關保港 全城抗疫】⚠️<br />\n鑑於香港政府應對武漢肺炎疫情態度消極，置前線醫護人員及市民於危難之間。<span style=\"color: red;\">聽日（1月30日）</span>會有<span style=\"color: red;\">十二個工會</span>係港、九、新界擺設街站，派發聯合傳單及白絲帶以表將會參加罷工的決心，與醫護、港人同行。 <span style=\"color: red;\">全城白絲帶，撐醫護，撐罷工！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以下工會當日會進行現場招收會員：</span></span><br />\n香港創建及工程人員總會<br />\n香港教育同行陣線<br />\n香港調酒師工會<br />\n香港白領（行政及文職）同行工會<br />\n香港會計專業人員協會<br />\n<br />\n**香港幼兒教育工會亦於31號同樣時間地點擺設街站。兩日（30日及31日）均不設現場招收會員，有仼何查詢或疑問歡迎當日到街站搵工會解答。<br />\n<br />\n#standwithmedics #standwithHAEA #封關保港 #全城抗疫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qD0Q0QK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqD0Q0QK.jpg&h=8bde2080&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g7aYqhq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg7aYqhq.jpg&h=e86ae594&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5e71ee7329ba86306214378459566ca29cfa08e","tid":1851920,"uid":104585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18462106045a553bb466c6fc0d5068fc82c30b3","tid":1851920,"uid":192983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:25:09.000Z","msg":"我和醫護一齊罷工"},{"pid":"cf69563e0b84d2359e3fecbd7b455098aa5832b7","tid":1851920,"uid":192983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:25:44.000Z","msg":"入工會大三罷支持醫護"},{"pid":"9c87d8e4555ae4c0652845491b97b08ecfed0563","tid":1851920,"uid":233030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:27:27.000Z","msg":"抗疫三罷"},{"pid":"fa1757d68cbd8f450492dd751866ffce6c14b686","tid":1851920,"uid":192983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:27:47.000Z","msg":"港人自救 不封關就罷工"},{"pid":"7b8550a8d5b506751309cd678c7ed3b663d7dbc9","tid":1851920,"uid":233030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:27:53.000Z","msg":"港共政府 草菅人命"},{"pid":"c20880c9be687ded8b3db0f56f2830eb63ac9c05","tid":1851920,"uid":192983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:28:17.000Z","msg":"抗疫三罷"},{"pid":"919ce12af20f5ccc47d1587913cd63ef63ce85ba","tid":1851920,"uid":233030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:28:18.000Z","msg":"抗疫三罷 封城救港"},{"pid":"7ad9475a37b27ab2b58ef85cec38d336119e105d","tid":1851920,"uid":233030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:28:38.000Z","msg":"Save HK"},{"pid":"9cd9d607db4a6ef9c68d5bf1426add0f8c7d0316","tid":1851920,"uid":41496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:28:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b806666f4a7759880175692f18c98edece967bc1","tid":1851920,"uid":192983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:29:11.000Z","msg":"入工會有保障大三罷救香港"},{"pid":"4074a3d73329280244e528e1dd0808ee0d2cda14","tid":1851920,"uid":233030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T08:29:17.000Z","msg":"⚠️工會大全⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=9c795a04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1IPQPGavm7k6saSj8fZ6J7QtblYdale6O9ddZg0bDEbQ/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n⚠️Group List⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/h